des:
Sunny 106 WDSN plays songs that pick you up and make you feel good! To enable our skill, say "Alexa, enable sunny one oh six skill."

Sunny 106 is available to stream throughout Pennsylvania and in most of New York, Ohio and West Virginia, but not all markets. If you don’t hear audio, it’s because Sunny 106 is not available in that market. Our apologies for any inconvenience. You can contact us at info@prioritymedia.net.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
